1. use $ sign to declare variables

2. use nesting
3. make partials with starting charcter underscore

4. use @import to include partial SCSS

5. use @extend .panel; to extend a class

6. use mixins for example
	use @mixin to create a mixin
	use @include to include a mixin

	@mixin border-radius($radius){
		-webkit-border-radius:$radius;
		-moz-border-radius:$radius;
		-ms-border-radiusL:$radius;(IE)
		border-radius:$radius;
	}


	.little-panel{
		@extend .panel;
		@include border-radius(5px);
		font-size: 12px;
	}
	
	.little-panel{
		@extend .panel;
		@include border-radius(25px);
		font-size: 32px;
	}

7. Operations

you can use addition,sub,mul div
